                <span class="text-[10px] text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">FORMAT SPEC</span>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase mt-2 mb-1">Multi-Format support</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-mute font-inter leading-relaxed">Combine PDFs, Word DOCX documents, PowerPoint PPTX presentations, and images simultaneously in one flow.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-neutral-800 bg-canvas/40 backdrop-blur-md p-5 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
              <div>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-primary uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">WORKSPACE SPEC</span>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase mt-2 mb-1">Incremental uploads</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-mute font-inter leading-relaxed">Append additional documents or images at any time without losing your current selections or reordered list.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-neutral-800 bg-canvas/40 backdrop-blur-md p-5 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
