                <p class="text-mute font-inter leading-relaxed">PageSlice makes removing pages from a PDF simple. Drag and drop your PDF file onto the page, check only the pages you want to keep, and then click the "Extract Selected Pages" button. The unchecked pages will be removed, creating a new PDF instantly on your device.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="border-b border-neutral-800/50 pb-6 text-left">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide mb-2"><span class="text-primary font-bold">Q /</span> Can I delete pages from a PDF?</h3>
